extends layout

block content
  h1 Learn about the <strong>pitfalls of  <br/>the legal documents</strong> of your favorite websites
  p.lead
    | All you need is
    | <a href="#{storeUrl}">download our extension</a>
    | from Chrome Web Store. <br/>The rest you will learn through our
    | <img src="http://bashmach.koding.io/img/icons/cold-38.png">
    |Termo-indicator.
  .row
    .col-sm-10.col-md-offset-1
      .carousel.slide(id="websites-carousel", data-ride="carousel")
        ol.carousel-indicators
          li.active(data-target="#websites-carousel", data-slide-to="0")
          li(data-target="#websites-carousel", data-slide-to="1")
          li(data-target="#websites-carousel", data-slide-to="2")

        .carousel-inner(role="listbox")
          .item.active
            img(src="/img/websites/facebook-carousel.png", alt="Popular website")
            .carousel-caption
              h3 Not every popular website has a clear legal documents

          .item
            img(src="/img/websites/stackoverflow-carousel.png", alt="On some resources they are very usual")
            .carousel-caption
              h3 On some resources they are very usual

          .item
            img(src="/img/websites/termos-carousel.png", alt="On others they are completely clear to everyone")
            .carousel-caption
              h3 On others they are completely clear to everyone ;)

        a.left.carousel-control(href="#websites-carousel", role="button", data-slide="prev")
            span.fa.fa-chevron-left.icon-prev(aria-hidden="true")
            span.sr-only
              | Previous
        a.right.carousel-control(href="#websites-carousel", role="button", data-slide="next")
            span.fa.fa-chevron-right.icon-next(aria-hidden="true")
            span.sr-only
              | Next

  hr
  .row
    .col-sm-12
      p.text-center
        a.btn.btn-success(href=storeUrl, role='button', target='_blank') Download from Chrome Web Store Â»
  hr
  .row
    .col-sm-12
      .text-center
        h4 Also you can scan any URL directly from here
        form.form-search.form-horizontal(action="/scan", method="post")
          input(type='hidden', name='_csrf', value=_csrf)
          .input-group.col-md-8.col-md-offset-2
            input.search-query.form-control(name="domain", type="text", placeholder="Scan website")
            span.input-group-btn
              button.btn(type="submit")
                i.fa.fa-search
            .clearfix
          p
            | For example:
            | <a href="http://bashmach.koding.io/scan/bashmach.koding.io">bashmach.koding.io</a> or <a href="http://bashmach.koding.io/scan/www.facebook.com">www.facebook.com</a>


